                <Cell text="개인정보파일명" font="normal 700 15px/normal &quot;Noto Sans KR Bold&quot;,&quot;NotoSansKR-Bold&quot;,&quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;"/>
                <Cell col="1" text="운영근거 / 처리목적" font="normal 700 15px/normal &quot;Noto Sans KR Bold&quot;,&quot;NotoSansKR-Bold&quot;,&quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;"/>
